{"tid":1567073,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"鴻福堂深水埗站分店有敢言大媽","createTime":"2019-09-14T01:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T05:25:09.000Z","uid":301911,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee741523e4c2f5d65d4b2b69fd6740cbb25c56f","tid":1567073,"uid":301911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:53:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190911&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=60033171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190911%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D60033171&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ2XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=d13ffe02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190911%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D60033171&h=07507f46\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190911&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=60033171</a><br />\n<br />\n【新增影片】鴻福堂（1446）女員工一句話，引軒然大波，更令其最新已被天貓等內地多個平台下架。<br />\n<br />\n周日，有軍裝警察到深水埗港鐵站巡視並截查年輕人，站內鴻福堂一名女員工，高呼「支持香港警察！」、「打死啲學生」，片段其後於網上瘋傳。同日晚上，鴻福堂迅速發聲明向公眾道歉，指公司十分正視有同事涉於工作期間「發表不恰當的個人言論」，會嚴肅跟進及加強培訓。<br />\n<br />\n不過，有關道歉得罪內地網民，指支持警員不是不當言論，《香港商報》指「部分公眾對鴻福堂的公告感到失望」，目前，鴻福堂在多個網絡平台被下架。隨後，鴻福堂於微博發公告稱，為早前的聲明引起誤解致歉，又指「堅持擁護『一國兩制』，繼續支持特區政府依法治港，恢復秩序，共促繁榮。」"},{"pid":"7d35f9c97209567b551633cd74b9c197c2982051","tid":1567073,"uid":45830,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:57:35.000Z","msg":"支持就支持，幹嗎要人打死學生？難道你是大媽別人就不能是學生？"},{"pid":"0be0db2a62994671ebc6f5f72a83be1e317ea0c5","tid":1567073,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那"},{"pid":"23cb1c7bdf4c21fe389200c90d5a80036e31fd77","tid":1567073,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T02:05:23.000Z","msg":"兩面唔係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd70ef4619e